
burneye2 objobf - x86/Linux ELF relocateable object obfuscator
=============================================================================

Just a very early version, do not expect it to work on anything larger than a
100 line C file.

Send comments to scut@team-teso.net.

Also read the manpage.

The graph output stuff may be interesting (visually at least :)

Also try to load the output objects in IDA.


